{"word":"H2637 - חָסֵר - châçêr - khaw-sare' - Be abated","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָסֵר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châçêr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-sare'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be abated"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குறைந்திரு, குறைந்துபோ, குறைவுபடு, வடிந்து கொண்டிரு, தேவை, தாழ்ச்சியடை, சிறியவனாகு, நிறைந்திரு, அநுபவி, தாகந்தீர்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to lack, to be without, to decrease, to be lacking, to have a need"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to lack"},{"paragraph":"2) to be lacking"},{"paragraph":"3) to diminish, to decrease"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to cause to lack"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil) to cause to be lacking"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>lack</i>; by implication to <i>fail</i>, <i>want</i>, <i>lessen: - </i>be abated, bereave, decrease, (cause to) fail, (have) lack, make lower, want."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2637 - חָסֵר - châçêr - khaw-sare'/2637\">H2637</a>, <a href=\"#/H2638 - חָסֵר - châçêr - khaw-sare'/2638\">H2638</a>, <a href=\"#/H2639 - חֶסֶר - cheçer - kheh'-ler/2639\">H2639</a>, <a href=\"#/H2640 - חֹסֶר - chôçer - kho'-ser/2640\">H2640</a>, <a href=\"#/H2641 - חַסְרָה - Chaçrâh - khas-raw'/2641\">H2641</a>, <a href=\"#/H2642 - חֶסְרֹון - cheçrôwn - khes-rone'/2642\">H2642</a>, <a href=\"#/H4270 - מַחְסֹור - machçôwr - makh-sore'/4270\">H4270</a>"}]}